commitResults.messageTitle: refactor: Changed name of bot from "Duke" to "Bill"
commitResults.messageBody: Removed all traces of "Duke" and changed all instances of "Duke" to "Bill" in source code; updated "EXPECTED.TXT" to reflect change in bot name;

commitResults.messageTitle: feature: Added echo feature to Bill
feature: Add echo feature to Bill
feat: store user input and echo when requested
commitResults.messageBody:
Add the ability to store whatever text entered by the user and display
them back to the user when requested

commitResults.messageTitle: feat: add marking tasks as done or not done on list view
commitResults.messageBody: Add ability to mark tasks in list of tasks as done or not done according to list index; add echo when marking and unmarking tasks

commitResults.messageTitle: refactor(Bill): shift string outputs to TaskManager
commitResults.messageBody:
Too much string code in Bill made code unreadable, shifted bulk of
interactive code with Task objects to Taskmanager, Bill now focuses on
regex for easier conditional statement readability

commitResults.messageTitle: refactor: add description getter function in Task.java
commitResults.messageBody:
Prevent TaskManager from directly accessing information in Task; update
TaskManager to use get function to access information in Task objects

commitResults.messageTitle: refactor(Bill): reformat regex indices to magic numbers when matching special commands
commitResults.messageBody:
Reformat regex indices as magic numbers for Mark and Unmark commands to
ensure command is not incorrectly called

commitResults.messageTitle: refactor(Bill, TaskManager): update Bill to recognise commands by startsWith
commitResults.messageBody:
Update Bill to read mark and unmark commands by checking trimmed input
with startsWith instead of regex

Update should make code more readable than with regex

commitResults.messageTitle: refactor(Bill): refactor variable line to userInput
commitResults.messageBody: Refactor line to userInput to improve human readability of code

commitResults.messageTitle: feat: add todo, deadline and event classes of task and their interactions
commitResults.messageBody:
Add todo class of task, which is invoked by starting command with "todo"

Add deadline class of task, which includes a String date, and is
invoked by starting command with "deadline"

Add event class of task, which includes starting and ending Strings,
and is invoked by starting command with "event"

Add classification at start of output to display type of task
Remove legacy code that included unused toString invocation

commitResults.messageTitle: test: add automated text-ui testing framework
